data.description: Mid-century classic was built by local lumberyard owner for his family and features gleaming original oak floors and a rambling ranch floor plan. 1967 sq/ft allows for 3 spacious bedrooms/2.5 baths, a formal dining room, and a cozy den with wood-burning fireplace.  Huge living room showcases floor to ceiling windows that bring the backyard in  and an efficient woodstove insert to keep things toasty. Tons of built in storage tucked into every room. Double city lot with R-3 zoning means you could likely add an ADU. Fenced backyard includes a large patio with brick built-in firepit. Second driveway offers RV parking or big toy storage.
